          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">If this unit’s IMAGIFIER model is the last model in this unit to die, for this unit&apos;s Act of Faith roll, roll an additional D6 and discard the lowest. Then, if it was successful, this unit Heals 2.</characteristic>
